{
  "_comment": [
    "Schema reference for deployed_base.json — the file P1.9 writes after",
    "deploying PrivacyRelayer, StealthAddressRegistry, and UniswapPrivacyWrapper",
    "to Base mainnet. The backend's P1.5 loader (see _load_deployed_addresses()",
    "in backend/server.py) reads a file at this exact shape from",
    "contracts/deployed_base.json (git-ignored; this .example is the committed",
    "documentation of the contract). Copy this file to deployed_base.json and",
    "fill the addresses, or set UPL_DEPLOYED_BASE_JSON to point elsewhere for",
    "tests. Only keys listed per chain are read; unknown chains/keys are ignored.",
    "",
    "Per-chain address keys the loader overrides:",
    "  privacy_relayer   — PrivacyRelayer.sol      (override only; static placeholder stays otherwise)",
    "  stealth_registry  — StealthAddressRegistry.sol (override only)",
    "  uniswap_wrapper   — UniswapPrivacyWrapper.sol (optional; None/unset => not deployed)",
    "",
    "Provenance keys (logged at startup, not used for routing):",
    "  chainId, deployedAt (ISO-8601), commit (git sha of the deploy run).",
    "",
    "Normalization in the loader: null / \"\" / \"0x0\" / zero-address all map",
    "to None, i.e. 'not deployed on this chain'. A real checksummed address",
    "(0x-prefixed, 40 hex chars) overrides the static placeholder as-is — the",
    "loader does NOT call Web3.to_checksum_address; P1.9 must write a checksummed",
    "address (Hardhat's contract.address is already checksummed)."
  ],
  "base": {
    "chainId": 8453,
    "deployedAt": "2026-06-30T00:00:00.000Z",
    "commit": "<git sha of the P1.9 deploy run>",
    "privacy_relayer": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000",
    "stealth_registry": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000",
    "uniswap_wrapper": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000"
  }
}
